---
title: Ginger Lemongrass Pork & Sesame Potatoes with Bacon Pear Salad & Mayo
description: Here’s a dish that surprises you at every turn. These aren’t just roasted taters; a nutty sesame coating brings layers of addictive seasoning. And this isn’t just a pork steak – a honey-soy and ginger-lemongrass mixture adds an intoxicating aroma and flavour. Plus, the pear and cucumber salad adds the perfect freshness to round it all out. Get ready to fall in love with this meal!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
